query:
SELECT
                api_key.id,
                api_key.account_id,
                api_key.name,
                api_key.created_at,
                api_key.accessed_at,
                account.email as account_email
            FROM api_key
            JOIN account ON api_key.account_id = account.id
            WHERE api_key.organization_id = $1 AND api_key.revoked_at IS NULL
            ORDER BY api_key.created_at DESC
